  Game information :
  ==================

  Rise of Nations carries the sweeping scope of epic historical turn-based 
  strategy games, but gives the quick decision-making of real-time games such as 
  Age of Empires. The game brings to life the entire sweep of human culture, from 
  the late Stone Age to modern-day technology - not just in warfare, but in city 
  building, trade, and diplomacy. You can move through the game timeline quickly 
  and have a satisfying game experience without playing for hours!
  
  Cross genre gameplay - Combining the speed of real-time gaming with the epic 
  scope of turn-based strategy games, &quot;Rise of Nations&quot; allows players to have a 
  fast and fun experience with the option to complete a game in under an hour. The 
  game's epic scope moves throughout eight historical epochs, tying together the 
  mysteries of ancient philosophy and wonders of the world. 
  
  
  Multiple victory conditions - Players succeed through non-military and 
  quasi-military strategies including espionage, political maneuvering, technology 
  races and population growth. Players can also choose to win through military 
  action. 
  
  
  Conquer the World - This unique, non-linear single-player campaign allows gamers 
  to play on a real map of the world and take over one territory at a time. 
  Victory in each territory gives players tribute, special resources or bonus 
  powers. 
  
  
  Lead one of 18 highly diverse nations - Players lead one of 18 nations, each 
  with its own distinctive nation powers and special units (Aztecs, Bantu, 
  British, Chinese, Egyptians, French, Germans, Greeks, Inca, Japanese, Koreans, 
  Maya, Mongols, Nubians, Romans, Russians, Spanish and Turks). 
  
  
  Installation Information : 
  ========================== 
  
  Just extract the archives and burn the .cue file with your favorite CD-Recording 
  software. Then copy the crack from CD to installation directory and enjoy !
